column5: Bob was in trouble. > He forgot his wedding anniversary. > His wife was really angry. > > She told him 'Tomorrow morning, I expect to find a gift in the driveway > that goes from 0 to 200 in less than 10 seconds, AND IT BETTER BE > THERE!!' > > The next morning Bob got up early and left for work. > > When his wife woke up she looked out the window and sure enough there > was a box gift-wrapped in the middle of the driveway. > > Confused, the wife put on her robe and ran out to the driveway, and > brought the box back in the house. > > She opened it and found a brand new bathroom scale. > > Bob has been missing since Friday. >
The girls at work were talking about a Bob. Poor guy lives in the dresser drawers. No idea what they meant.
Funny, I thought Bob was a guy with no arms or legs floating in the water
